* 任务

- Task 1: 签署 CLA
- Task 2: 加入 Kubernetes Slack 频道 #kubernetes-users, #kubernetes-dev, #cn-dev and one of SIGs
- Task 3: 订阅 kubernetes-dev@googlegroups.com / https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/kubernetes-dev
- Task 4: https://github.com/kubernetes-sigs/contributor-playground 上创建一个 Issue 和一个 PR 并实验 @k8s-ci-robot 命令

